	<h1 class="title">新年工作利器推荐，这里有15个靠谱的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">利器</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-13 15:22:13 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20388/medium/20388.jpg?1452261527" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


